{"tid":1157422,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"唔介意你唔係處女 就代表真係愛？","createTime":"2019-05-16T09:24:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-16T15:32:09.000Z","uid":201604,"like":40,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"822f6c55a6d67fe51eea8ce7fb41ea67d0fc131f","tid":1157422,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T09:24:14.000Z","msg":"好多人都會覺得<br />\n佢連我唔係處都可以唔介意 一定係好愛我先會咁做<br />\n但人係有佔有慾 <br />\n又點會想第一次呢個位係畀其他人佔有左<br />\n如果唔係真心鍾意你 屌完就算 咪唔介意囉<br />\n<br />\n如果你話唔夠愛所以先介意 咁你就錯撚晒<br />\n就係因為在意你先至介意<br />\n但知你唔係處 都肯接受你 咁先真係愛<br />\n如果唔愛 佢大可以搵過個<br />\n仲使乜晒心機落你到 又搞到自己勁矛盾<br />\n<br />\n接受同介意係並存 既然你唔係處 唯有對佢好啲 等佢更加鍾意你"},{"pid":"0a113f8938682c10ea6cdeb94efce1635efbc16d","tid":1157422,"uid":146299,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T09:24:43.000Z","msg":"屌完二手西就會飛"},{"pid":"148707313f8e498ce3000d9a096e91079ee5ff7c","tid":1157422,"uid":146299,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T09:25:04.000Z","msg":"我要浮雲<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d60522d17f49d9b4d19b23278ea46fb1739a449","tid":1157422,"uid":8572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a113f8938682c10ea6cdeb94efce1635efbc16d","tid":1157422,"uid":146299,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T09:24:43.000Z","msg":"屌完二手西就會飛"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T09:25:22.000Z","msg":"U Mk jai"},{"pid":"1f0f6fa69efc64535c886e6695cbd71779694b8a","tid":1157422,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"148707313f8e498ce3000d9a096e91079ee5ff7c","tid":1157422,"uid":146299,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T09:25:04.000Z","msg":"我要浮雲<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T09:25:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bba483c143339bf81674271433420efa7bfbc7b","tid":1157422,"uid":18